Package src.Type

Interface grammarTCLListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public interface grammarTCLListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by grammarTCLParser.
